# Project Rule: F2 Planning (End-to-End)

## Inputs (In)
- F1 outputs: `docs/discovery/brief.md`, `docs/discovery/rad.md`

## Outputs (Out)
- `docs/planning/prd.md`
- `PLAN.md` (updated)
- `tasks-frontend.md`, `tasks-backend.md`
- `.cursor/dev-workflow/slices.yaml`
- `reports/audit-planning-<sessionId>-<ts>.md`
- `reports/validation-planning-<sessionId>-<ts>.md`

## Protocol
1. Finalize PRD; update PLAN with FE/BE slice plan and contracts.
2. Generate FE/BE tasks files; define slices.yaml with contractsVersion.
3. Auditor/Validator loop for GO decision.

## Acceptance
- PRD complete; tasks and slices present.
- Validation = GO; no Disagree items.

